      *****************************************************
JW9   * WRITE LOG FILE
      *****************************************************
     C           #LOG      BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         ACCRTM
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    ACCRUS
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    ACCRGM
